---

<section id="why" style="max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:76px 28px 20px">
  <p style="font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin:0 0 16px">Why AgentQuilt</p>
  <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.8vw,38px);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.025em;margin:0 0 16px;line-height:1.12;max-width:720px">One big agent file. A whole team editing it. Constant conflicts.</h2>
  <p style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 32px;max-width:660px">
    Large agent instruction files are hard to maintain in distributed teams. Two people editing the same prompt hit merge conflicts that are painful to resolve &mdash; agent instructions are semantic, not purely syntactic. And the same rules, copied by hand into Claude&rsquo;s <span style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:.9em;color:var(--fg)">CLAUDE.md</span>, OpenAI&rsquo;s <span style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:.9em;color:var(--fg)">AGENTS.md</span>, and more, quietly drift apart.
  </p>

  <!-- source fragment anchor -->
  <div style="margin-bottom:12px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid var(--accent);border-radius:10px;padding:13px 18px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:13px">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex:none;margin-top:2px"><path d="M6 3h8l4 4v14H6Z"/><path d="M14 3v4h4"/><path d="M9 12h6"/><path d="M9 16h5"/></svg>
    <div>
      <p style="font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:var(--faint);margin:0 0 5px">source fragment &middot; <span style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:11px">_shared/040-review-policy.md</span></p>
      <p style="font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--muted);margin:0">&ldquo;All PRs require two approvals and a green CI run before merge.&rdquo;</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- connector -->
  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px;padding-left:18px">
    <div style="width:1px;height:18px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--border),transparent)"></div>
    <p style="font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:var(--faint);margin:0">copied into 4 platform files &darr;</p>
  </div>

  <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;align-items:stretch">

    <!-- card 1: partial · faint amber border -->
    <div style="flex:1 1 220px;min-width:200px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid rgba(224,160,106,.4);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:11px">
        <span style="width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:2px;background:#e0a06a;flex:none"></span>
        <span style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--fg)">CLAUDE.md</span>
        <span style="margin-left:auto;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap">Claude Code</span>
      </div>
      <p style="font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--faint);margin:0 0 14px;flex:1">&ldquo;Require two approvals before merge.&rdquo;</p>
      <span style="align-self:flex-start;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#e0a06a;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb,#e0a06a 35%,transparent);border-radius:99px;padding:3px 8px">partial &middot; 2d ago</span>
    </div>

    <!-- card 2: contradicts · medium amber border -->
    <div style="flex:1 1 220px;min-width:200px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid rgba(224,160,106,.65);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:11px">
        <span style="width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:2px;background:#5aa9f0;flex:none"></span>
        <span style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--fg)">AGENTS.md</span>
        <span style="margin-left:auto;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap">OpenAI Codex</span>
      </div>
      <p style="font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--faint);margin:0 0 14px;flex:1">&ldquo;One approval is fine &mdash; move fast.&rdquo;</p>
      <span style="align-self:flex-start;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#e0a06a;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb,#e0a06a 35%,transparent);border-radius:99px;padding:3px 8px">contradicts &middot; 3w ago</span>
    </div>

    <!-- card 3: reworded · orange border -->
    <div style="flex:1 1 220px;min-width:200px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid rgba(220,120,70,.82);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:11px">
        <span style="width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:2px;background:#4fd0ff;flex:none"></span>
        <span style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--fg)">reviewer.md</span>
        <span style="margin-left:auto;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap">Claude subagent</span>
      </div>
      <p style="font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--faint);margin:0 0 14px;flex:1">&ldquo;Two approvals, plus a security pass.&rdquo;</p>
      <span style="align-self:flex-start;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#e0a06a;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb,#e0a06a 35%,transparent);border-radius:99px;padding:3px 8px">reworded &middot; 5w ago</span>
    </div>

    <!-- card 4: omitted · vivid red border -->
    <div style="flex:1 1 220px;min-width:200px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:3px solid rgba(210,70,60,.88);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:11px">
        <span style="width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:2px;background:#b48cf0;flex:none"></span>
        <span style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;color:var(--fg)">SKILL.md</span>
        <span style="margin-left:auto;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap">Agent Skills</span>
      </div>
      <p style="font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--faint);margin:0 0 14px;flex:1">&ldquo;(review policy not mentioned)&rdquo;</p>
      <span style="align-self:flex-start;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#e07070;border:1px solid color-mix(in srgb,#e07070 35%,transparent);border-radius:99px;padding:3px 8px">omitted &middot; 2mo ago</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
